 814}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"gender controversy|GETTYAfter\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"just 46 seconds\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking afterwards, she said: \\\"I have never felt a punch like this.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a punch\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got into the ring to fight.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not give up, but one punch hurt too much and so I said enough.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one punch\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going out with my head held high.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the second punch, after years of experience, I felt a strong pain in the nose.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second punch\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong pain\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the nose\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said enough, because I did not want.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not finish the fight after the punch to the nose.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"the punch\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"the nose\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it was better to put an end to it.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She added: \\\"Even if they had said that we would not fight, I would never have accepted it.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a warrior's mentality.\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warrior's mentality\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time I did not manage.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt too much pain on my nose.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"too much pain\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"my nose\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said enough.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a defeat for me - for me if you go in the ring you have already won, regardless of everything else.JUST IN:Harry Redknapp's \\u00a35million Dorset home BURGLED as wife Sandra's jewellery targeted\\\"I am not here to judge.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"score\": 0.9695553924689311, \"rank\": 0.018423832802238502, \"text\": \"Sandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a defeat\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not up to me to say if it's fair or not fair.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\"